ar school noun","the grammar translation method noun","grammatical adjective","grammatically adverb"]},{"name":"grammar school","pos":"noun","content":"<div class=\"entry\" hclass=\"entry\" sum=\"448\" sk=\"grammarschool: :0\" hlength=\"14\" id=\"grammar-school\" htag=\"section\" idm_id=\"000025836\"><div class=\"top-container\"><div class=\"top-g\" id=\"grammar_school_topg_1\"><div class=\"webtop\"><h1 class=\"headword\" id=\"grammar_school_h_1\" htag=\"h1\" hclass=\"headword\">grammar school</h1> <span class=\"pos\" hclass=\"pos\" htag=\"span\">noun</span><span class=\"phonetics\"> <div class=\"phons_br\" geo=\"br\" htag=\"div\" hclass=\"phons_br\" wd=\"grammar school\"><div class=\"sound audio_play_button pron-uk icon-audio\" data-src-mp3=\"https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/media/english/uk_pron/g/gra/gramm/grammar_school_1_gb_1.mp3\" data-src-ogg=\"https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/media/english/uk_pron_ogg/g/gra/gramm/grammar_school_1_gb_1.ogg\" title=\"grammar school pronunciation\n                    English\" style=\"cursor: pointer\" valign=\"top\">&nbsp;</div><span class=\"phon\">/ˈɡræmə skuːl/</span></div> <div class=\"phons_n_am\" wd=\"grammar school\" hclass=\"phons_n_am\" geo=\"n_am\" htag=\"div\"><div class=\"sound audio_play_button pron-us icon-audio\" data-src-mp3=\"https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/media/english/us_pron/g/gra/gramm/grammar_school_1_us_1.mp3\" data-src-ogg=\"https://www.oxfordlearnersdictionaries.com/media/english/us_pron_ogg/g/gra/gramm/grammar_school_1_us_1.ogg\" title=\"grammar school pronunciation\n                    American\" style=\"cursor: pointer\" valign=\"top\">&nbsp;</div><span class=\"phon\">/ˈɡræmər skuːl/</span></div></span> </div><a class=\"responsive_display_inline_on_smartphone link-right\" href=\"#relatedentries\">\n                            jump to other results\n                        </a></div></div><ol class=\"senses_multiple\" htag=\"ol\"><li class=\"sense\" sensenum=\"1\" hclas